{
  "id": "adv_group_thrx_01_01",
  "title": "IIIX 01 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "（高校生の頃、初めてアイドルのライブを観に行った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When I was in high school‚ I went to an idol live for the first time.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなに笑顔を届けて、観客を熱狂させて）\n（今までに見たどんなものよりキラキラして見えた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(They brought smiles to everyone's faces‚ made the audience go wild‚)\n(and they looked more dazzling than anything I'd ever seen.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "（世の中には、こんな人達もいるんだと思ったっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I thought‚ \"There are people like this in the world.\")",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "（……今は、私もその『アイドル』なのだけれど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…And now‚ I'm also an \"idol\".)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5466.6666667,
          "startTime": 24.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITY決勝から少し経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after the I-UNITY finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2399.9999999999986,
          "startTime": 27.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……あら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh my.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、スリクスのみなさん……！？\n……こ、こんな所でお会いするとは思いませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if it isn't IIIX…?\nI… I never expected to see you here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "私達もです\nここ最近、何かと慌ただしかったですものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We didn't expect this either.\nThings have been quite hectic lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれは慌ただしいなんてもんじゃ……\n……そうですよね、大変でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hectic is an understatement…\n…That's right‚ it must have been tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは、{user}さんに\n橋本さん……で良かったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good afternoon‚ {user}-san and\nHashimoto-san… is that right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "お二人とも、星見プロのマネージャーさんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're both managers at Hoshimi Pro‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ご無沙汰しております！\n改めまして、星見プロダクションの橋本でっす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it's been a while!\nI'm Satomi Hashimoto from Hoshimi Productions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "このカフェ、すぐ隣がテレビ局ですから\nよく業界の人も使ってますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This cafe is right next to the TV station‚\nso it's often used by people in the industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "私達はさっき番組の収録が終わったばかりで……\n橋本さん達は、打ち合わせか何かで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We just finished recording for a TV show…\nAre you here for a meeting or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes! That's right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、星見プロの敏腕マネージャーさん達に\nお会いしました！　ってSNSに上げていいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ can I post on social media that I met\nHoshimi Pro's amazing managers?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に写真も撮っちゃいましょう！！\nもちろん、ちゃんと顔はデコって隠しますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's take a picture together!!\nOf course‚ I'll cover your faces with stickers!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "どんな感じにデコっちゃいます？\nkanaは、このウサギさんがイチオシなんですけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of stickers should we use?\nI like this bunny one~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……い、いやあ。しがないマネージャーを\nあまりからかわないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well… please don't tease\na humble manager like me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ちぇっ\n絶対『いいね』稼げると思ったのになあ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tch.\nI thought it would get a lot of likes~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……kana、そのくらいにしておきなさい\n{user}さんが困っているでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kana‚ that's enough.\nYou're making {user}-san uncomfortable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "は～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……星見プロのみなさんには、先日のイベントで\n素晴らしいステージを観せていただきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We were treated to a wonderful performance by Hoshimi Pro\nat the recent event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "また近いうちに、お会い出来たら嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We hope to see you again soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
